Package mumble.nooko3.sdk.NKClient.NKApiResultsLIsteners

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NKApiBlockResultListener
    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForBlock(Context, long, boolean), and similar, methods, returns a NKBlock if all went right or an error message if something went wrong
    NKApiBlocksResultListener
    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForBlocks(Context, ArrayList, boolean)}, and similar, methods, returns an ArrayList of NKBlock if all went right or an error message if something went wrong
    NKApiElementsResultListener
    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForSections(Context, long, ArrayList, boolean), and similar, methods, returns an ArrayList of NKSection if all went right or an error message if something went wrong
    NKApiProjectResultListener
    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForProject(Context), and similar, methods, returns a NKProject if all went right or an error message if something went wrong
    NKApiSectionResultListener
    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForSection(Context, long, boolean), and similar, methods, returns a NKSection if all went right or an error message if something went wrong
    NKApiSectionsResultListener
    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForSections(Context, long, ArrayList, boolean), and similar, methods, returns an ArrayList of NKSection if all went right or an error message if something went wrong

    Interface to use with Nooko3Tasks.askForProject(Context), and similar, methods, returns a NKProject if all went right or an error message if something went wrong
